title: Sharepoint permission to create public views
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

In order to restrict users from creating public views for [[Sharepoint lists|Sharepoint list]], remove this access:

```
Manage Lists  -  Create and delete lists, add or remove columns in a list, and add or remove public views of a list.
```